radiographic_examinations.findings: Generalized osteopenia, Wormian bones, several lateral rib fractures with callus formation, acute oblique right humerus fracture, and bowing and thickening of the bilateral femurs. Markedly thin cortex with hypercellular woven bony trabeculae. Healing fractures with irregularly arranged trabeculae and callus formation of woven bone and cartilaginous proliferation.
